{"title":"数据结构代码实现：顺序查找,二分查找,KMP算法","uid":"1ed24a617f1cbb7cd98bc55a230d31e9","slug":"DataStructure-KMP","date":"2020-05-18T11:57:32.000Z","updated":"2020-05-19T14:18:21.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/DataStructure-KMP.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200518195818.png","content":"<h2 id=\"存储结构定义\"><a href=\"#存储结构定义\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"存储结构定义\"></a>存储结构定义</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">#define ElemType int\ntypedef char* SString;\n&#x2F;&#x2F;顺序表的定义\ntypedef struct &#123;\n    ElemType *elem;&#x2F;&#x2F;数据\n    int TableLen;&#x2F;&#x2F;长度\n&#125;SSTable;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"顺序查找\"><a href=\"#顺序查找\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"顺序查找\"></a>顺序查找</h2><ul>\n<li>在顺序表中顺序查找关键字为key的元素，若找到则返回该元素在表中的位置<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">int Search_Seq(SSTable ST,ElemType key)&#123;\n    ST.elem[0]&#x3D;key;\n    int i;\n    for(i&#x3D;ST.TableLen;ST.elem[i]!&#x3D;key;--i);\n    return i;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"二分查找\"><a href=\"#二分查找\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二分查找\"></a>二分查找</h2></li>\n<li>二分法的前提是查找有序表</li>\n<li>算法思路为：<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>将要查找的元素与表中中间的元素比较，若相等，则查找成功,返回元素所在位置，若大于中间元素，则要查找的元素一定在后半部分，若小于中间元素，则要查找的颜色一定在前半部分。然后缩小范围继续用同样的方法查找，直到找到为止。<br><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200518201131.png\" alt=\"二分查找\"></p></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">int Binary_Search(SSTable L,ElemType key)&#123;\n    int low&#x3D;0,high&#x3D;L.TableLen-1,mid;\n    while(low&lt;&#x3D;high)&#123;\n        mid&#x3D;(low+high)&#x2F;2;\n        if(L.elem[mid]&#x3D;&#x3D;key)&#123;\n            return mid;\n        &#125;else if(L.elem[mid]&gt;key)&#123;\n            high&#x3D;mid-1;\n        &#125;else&#123;\n            low&#x3D;mid+1;\n        &#125;\n    &#125;\n    return -1;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"字符串的模式匹配\"><a href=\"#字符串的模式匹配\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"字符串的模式匹配\"></a>字符串的模式匹配</h2></li>\n<li>算法思想：<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>从主串S的第pos个字符开始，与模式的第一个字符比较，若相等，则继续逐个比较后续字符，否则从主串的下一个字符起，重新和模式的字符比较，以此类推，直到模式T中的每个字符依次和主串S中的一个连续字符序列相等，则匹配成功<br><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200518210605.png\" alt=\"字符串的模式匹配\"></p></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">int Index(SString S,SString T)&#123;\n    int i&#x3D;1,j&#x3D;1;\n    while (i&lt;&#x3D;S[0]&amp;&amp;j&lt;&#x3D;T[0])&#123;\n        if(S[i]&#x3D;&#x3D;T[j])&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;继续比较后继字符\n            ++i;\n            ++j;\n        &#125;else&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;指针后退重新开始匹配\n            i&#x3D;i-j+2;\n            j&#x3D;1;\n        &#125;\n    &#125;\n    if(j&gt;T[0])&#123;\n        return i-T[0];\n    &#125;else&#123;\n        return 0;\n    &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"KMP算法\"><a href=\"#KMP算法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"KMP算法\"></a>KMP算法</h2><p><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200518230418.png\"></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">void get_next(char T[],int next[])&#123;\n    int i&#x3D;1;\n    next[1]&#x3D;0;\n    int j&#x3D;0;\n    while (i&lt;T[0])&#123;\n        if(j&#x3D;&#x3D;0||T[i]&#x3D;&#x3D;T[j])&#123;\n            ++i;\n            ++j;\n            next[i]&#x3D;j;\n        &#125;else&#123;\n            j&#x3D;next[j];\n        &#125;\n    &#125;\n&#125;\nint KMP(char S[],char T[],int next[],int pos)&#123;\n    int i&#x3D;pos;\n    int j&#x3D;1;\n    while (i&lt;&#x3D;S[0]&amp;&amp;j&lt;&#x3D;T[0])&#123;\n        if(j&#x3D;&#x3D;0||S[i]&#x3D;&#x3D;T[j])&#123;\n            ++i;\n            ++j;\n        &#125;else&#123;\n            j&#x3D;next[j];\n        &#125;\n    &#125;\n\n    if(j&gt;T[0])&#123;\n        return i-T[0];\n    &#125;else&#123;\n        return 0;\n    &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre>","text":"存储结构定义#define ElemType int typedef char* SString; &#x2F;&#x2F;顺序表的定义 typedef struct &#123; ElemType *elem;&#x2F;&#x2F;数据 int TableLen;&#x2F;...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.3k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":11,"path":"api/categories/数据结构.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":11,"path":"api/tags/数据结构.json"},{"name":"C++","slug":"C","count":11,"path":"api/tags/C.json"},{"name":"考研","slug":"考研","count":11,"path":"api/tags/考研.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"t